      "text": [
        "هُ قَالَ لَا أَقْبَلُ شَهَادَةَ الْفَاسِقِ إِلَّا عَلَى نَفْسِهِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Isa, from Al Husayn Bin Saeed, from Al Qasim Bin Suleyman, from Jarrah Al Madainy, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The testimony of the immoral cannot be accepted except against himself (confession)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. A number of our people have narrated from ands from al-Husayn ibn Sa‘id from al-Qasim ibn Sulayman from Jarrah al-Mad’iniy who has narrated the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘I do not accept the testimony of a sinful man except against his own-self.’” "
        ]
      }
